OL,3,CSerena Williams handed wild card for
OL,4,Cwomen's singles at Wimbledon
OL,6,FSerena Williams has been handed a wild
OL,7,Fcard to play in the women's singles at
OL,8,FWimbledon.
OL,10,FThe 44-year-old had already been given
OL,11,Fa wild card into the doubles alongside
OL,12,Fsister Venus after ending a four-year
OL,13,Fspell away from tennis by beginning
OL,14,Fher comeback at Queen's Club.
OL,16,FBut the seven-time Wimbledon singles
OL,17,Fchampion will now take her place in
OL,18,Fthe individual event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
