OL,3,CSerena Williams handed wild card for
OL,4,Cwomen's singles at Wimbledon
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA post on Wimbledon's X account on
OL,12,FSunday evening read: "This is not a
OL,13,Fdrill. @serenawilliams will compete in
OL,14,Fthe 2026 ladies' singles at _Wimbledon
OL,15,Fas a wild card."
OL,17,FWilliams, who has won a record 23
OL,18,Fwomen's major singles titles in the
OL,19,FOpen era, ended her absence from the
OL,20,Fmatch court in doubles at Queen's
OL,21,Fearlier this month.
