OL,3,CSerena Williams handed wild card for
OL,4,Cwomen's singles at Wimbledon
OL,6,FShe won her first contest alongside
OL,7,FVictoria Mboko before the Canadian's
OL,8,Finjury curtailed their run.
OL,10,FWilliams then headed to Berlin but
OL,11,Fsuffered a first-round loss at the WTA
OL,12,FTour event playing with Karolina
OL,13,FMuchova.
